# ============================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT TIPS
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Create separate values files for each environment:
#    - values-dev.yaml (for development with "develop" tag)
#    - values-main.yaml (for main branch with "release" tag)
#    - values-prod.yaml (for production with version tags like "v1.0.0")
#
# 2. Install with specific values:
#    helm install my-girok-web-girok . -f values.yaml -f values-prod.yaml
#
# 3. Harbor Registry:
#    - Images are stored at harbor.girok.dev/my-girok/web-girok
#    - Tag "develop" for develop branch deployments
#    - Tag "release" for main branch deployments
#    - Tag "v1.0.0" style for production releases
#
# 4. Frontend considerations:
#    - Static files are served via Nginx
#    - API URL is configured at build time (VITE_API_URL)
#    - For multiple environments, build separate images
#    - Consider using CDN for static assets in production
#
# ============================================================================
